    <title>tree</title>
    <link href="/2024/10/19/tree/"/>
    <url>/2024/10/19/tree/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1tZ421q72h?spm_id_from=333.788.videopod.sections&vd_source=b7c43e8599d7b18c8d7a18d36ee79de0">平衡二叉树(AVL树)_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a><br>这里指的是二叉树。<br>二叉树的特点在于查找数据的时候效率是O(log n)，和数组里的二分查找一样。但是它还可以解决数组中删除和插入是O(n)的问题。<br>对于AVL树，满足|左子树深度-右子树深度|&lt;&#x3D;1。<br>这样是为了防止树糟糕地退化成链表的形状，左右失衡，影响效率。<br>在插入数据的时候，有左旋右旋的操作。<br>以下是代码实现。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br><span class="line">109</span><br><span class="line">110</span><br><span class="line">111</span><br><span class="line">112</span><br><span class="line">113</span><br><span class="line">114</span><br><span class="line">115</span><br><span class="line">116</span><br><span class="line">117</span><br><span class="line">118</span><br><span class="line">119</span><br><span class="line">120</span><br><span class="line">121</span><br><span class="line">122</span><br><span class="line">123</span><br><span class="line">124</span><br><span class="line">125</span><br><span class="line">126</span><br><span class="line">127</span><br><span class="line">128</span><br><span class="line">129</span><br><span class="line">130</span><br><span class="line">131</span><br><span class="line">132</span><br><span class="line">133</span><br><span class="line">134</span><br><span class="line">135</span><br><span class="line">136</span><br><span class="line">137</span><br><span class="line">138</span><br><span class="line">139</span><br><span class="line">140</span><br><span class="line">141</span><br><span class="line">142</span><br><span class="line">143</span><br><span class="line">144</span><br><span class="line">145</span><br><span class="line">146</span><br><span class="line">147</span><br><span class="line">148</span><br><span class="line">149</span><br><span class="line">150</span><br><span class="line">151</span><br><span class="line">152</span><br><span class="line">153</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">typedef</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title">Node</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> value;<br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title">Node</span>* <span class="hljs-title">left</span>;</span><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title">Node</span>* <span class="hljs-title">right</span>;</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> height; <span class="hljs-comment">//高度，用来计算平衡因子</span><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> balfactor; <span class="hljs-comment">//平衡因子</span><br>&#125;node;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">max</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>(a &gt; b ? a : b); &#125; <span class="hljs-comment">//比大小</span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">height</span><span class="hljs-params">(node* n)</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">//返回每一个结点的高</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> n-&gt;height;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">upheightbal</span><span class="hljs-params">(node* n)</span> &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">//更新结点的高和平衡因子</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)<br>&#123;<br>n-&gt;height = max(height(n-&gt;left), height(n-&gt;right)) + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>n-&gt;balfactor = height(n-&gt;left) - height(n-&gt;right);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">leftturn</span><span class="hljs-params">(node** n)</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">rightturn</span><span class="hljs-params">(node** n)</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">jugde</span><span class="hljs-params">(node** n)</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//判断失衡现象</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;balfactor == <span class="hljs-number">2</span> &amp;&amp; (*n)-&gt;left-&gt;balfactor == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)rightturn(n);       <span class="hljs-comment">//LL型</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;balfactor &gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span> &amp;&amp; (*n)-&gt;left-&gt;balfactor == <span class="hljs-number">-1</span>)                  <span class="hljs-comment">//LR型</span><br>&#123;<br>leftturn(&amp;((*n)-&gt;left));<br>rightturn(n);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;balfactor == <span class="hljs-number">-2</span> &amp;&amp; (*n)-&gt;right-&gt;balfactor == <span class="hljs-number">-1</span>)leftturn(n);<span class="hljs-comment">//RR型</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;balfactor &lt; <span class="hljs-number">-1</span> &amp;&amp; (*n)-&gt;right-&gt;balfactor == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)                 <span class="hljs-comment">//RL型</span><br>&#123;<br>rightturn(&amp;((*n)-&gt;right));<br>leftturn(n);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><br>node* <span class="hljs-title function_">insert</span><span class="hljs-params">(node* n, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val)</span> &#123;  <span class="hljs-comment">//创建结点同时判断旋转情况（kimi指导使用递归即判断旋转）</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)<br>&#123;<br>node* newnode = (node*)<span class="hljs-built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">sizeof</span>(node));<br>newnode-&gt;value = val;<br>newnode-&gt;left = newnode-&gt;right = <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>;<br>newnode-&gt;height = newnode-&gt;balfactor = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> newnode;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n-&gt;value &gt; val)        n-&gt;left = insert(n-&gt;left, val);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n-&gt;value &lt; val)n-&gt;right = insert(n-&gt;right, val);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>                        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> n;<br><br>upheightbal(n);<br>jugde(&amp;n);<br>upheightbal(n);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> n;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">leftturn</span><span class="hljs-params">(node** n)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//左旋</span><br>&#123;<br>upheightbal(*n);<br>node* temp1 = *n;<br>node* temp2 = (*n)-&gt;right-&gt;left;<br>*n = (*n)-&gt;right;<br>(*n)-&gt;left = temp1;<br>(*n)-&gt;left-&gt;right = temp2;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">rightturn</span><span class="hljs-params">(node** n)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//右旋</span><br>&#123;<br>node* temp1 = (*n);<br>node* temp2 = (*n)-&gt;left-&gt;right;<br>*n = (*n)-&gt;left;<br>(*n)-&gt;right = temp1;<br>(*n)-&gt;right-&gt;left = temp2;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">qianxu</span><span class="hljs-params">(node* n)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//前序读取</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>, n-&gt;value);<br>qianxu(n-&gt;left);<br>qianxu(n-&gt;right);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">zhongxu</span><span class="hljs-params">(node* n)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//中序读取</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)<br>&#123;<br>zhongxu(n-&gt;left);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>, n-&gt;value);<br>zhongxu(n-&gt;right);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">houxu</span><span class="hljs-params">(node* n)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//后序读取</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)<br>&#123;<br>houxu(n-&gt;left);<br>houxu(n-&gt;right);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>, n-&gt;value);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">get</span><span class="hljs-params">(node** n, node* temp)</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//辅助删除函数的实现（递归）</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (*n != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)<br>&#123;<br>get(n, temp);<span class="hljs-comment">//递归</span><br>upheightbal(*n);<span class="hljs-comment">//等到完成“嫁接”工作后要重新更新一下高度</span><br>jugde(n);<span class="hljs-comment">//判断要不要旋转</span><br>upheightbal(*n);<span class="hljs-comment">//旋转后还要更新高度，也确保之后父结点的高度更新正确</span><br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (*n == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>) &#123;<br>*n = temp;<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Delete</span><span class="hljs-params">(node** n, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> data)</span><span class="hljs-comment">//删除结点的函数（非懒惰删除）</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (*n == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>)  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;value &gt; data)Delete(&amp;((*n)-&gt;left), data);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;value &lt; data)Delete(&amp;((*n)-&gt;right), data);<span class="hljs-comment">//两个递归</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;value == data) &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;left == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span> &amp;&amp; (*n)-&gt;right == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>) &#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//没有孩子的结点（树叶）</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">free</span>(*n);<br>*n = <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;left == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span> &amp;&amp; (*n)-&gt;right != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>) &#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//有右孩子的结点</span><br>node* temp = *n;<br>*n = (*n)-&gt;right;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">free</span>(temp);<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;right == <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span> &amp;&amp; (*n)-&gt;left != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>) &#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//有左孩子的结点</span><br>node* temp = *n;<br>*n = (*n)-&gt;left;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">free</span>(temp);<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((*n)-&gt;left != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span> &amp;&amp; (*n)-&gt;right != <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>) &#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//左右孩子都有</span><br>node* temp = (*n)-&gt;left;<span class="hljs-comment">//先保存左支防失联</span><br>node* temp2 = *n;<br>*n = (*n)-&gt;right;<span class="hljs-comment">//用右孩子替换要删除的结点</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">free</span>(temp2);<br>get(n, temp);<span class="hljs-comment">//开始递归寻找存放左支的地方并记录路径</span><br>&#125;<br>upheightbal(*n);<span class="hljs-comment">//这是为前三种情况准备的</span><br>jugde(n);<span class="hljs-comment">//删除之后，找到要删除结点的路径上的结点都要重新判别失衡现象</span><br>upheightbal(*n);<span class="hljs-comment">//转完还要更新</span><br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上代码完成了AVL树插入时旋转的平衡操作，以及附加了一般树的前中后序遍历。<br>比较重要的是其中对树遍历（包括查找和删除）时使用的递归操作（递归虽说效率不高，但对晕树来说是很好理解与实现的方式了）。<br>在insert操作中，传入的node* root，对于指针来说是值传递（唉），因此如果在函数中将形参指向新开辟的空间的话，root的指向是不会变。因此这里使用了返回指针的操作来对root进行重新赋值；<br>然后是node**这个东西，也和值传递有关，因为值传递无法改变实参，所以要地址传递，便有了这种写法，把指向node地址的指针的地址传送过去（<del>但是一直要写(*n)好烦啊！</del>），主要在turn和Delete函数中使用，因为它们要对树的结构进行修改。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
